Mapazi e[[Hugabe]] (Responsible Authorities) - pakushanda kunoita [[hushangazhi]] pane mapazi ehurumende akapiwa [[hudaviri]] ne[[hugabe]] (responsibility; authority) kuti ave anotarira kuti mitemo yakasiyana yehurumende yatevedzwa.  Mapazi e'''hugabe''' aya anobata basa zvichienderana nemitemo yakatarwa nedare reParamende - (Acts of Parliament). MuZimbabwe kune Mapazi e'''hugabe''' anoti: Zimra; Zimre; Zinwa; Zinara; Municipalities; Natural Resources Board; Environmental Protection Authority zvichingodaro.  '''Hugabe''', izwi rinotodza shoko rokuti '''ubugabe''' rinobva ku[[Mutauro]] wechi[[Bantu]] unotaurwa kunyika yeBurundi unonzi Kirundi.  '''Ubugabe''', zvinoreva '''authority'''.


Nokumwe kutaura tingati '''hugabe''' isimba rakapiwa pasi pemitemo yenyika kuti munhu kana boka revanhu rive neutongi pamusoro pemabatirwo ezvinhu zvinosanganisira: vanhu; basa; mari; ivhu; michero, zvichingodaro. Hapana kusarudzwa izwi rokuti '''simba''' nokuti iri izwi rinoreva zvakawanda zvinosanganisira: ''power; energy; force; authority; might; strength'' zvichingodaro.
